metadata.name: Explore yourself
metadata.description:
"Please, keep looking. Not for a person, but for your passion, your love, your courage, your goals, your dreams, your happiness, yourself. Explore yourself, before you explore another. Know your worth, know yourself. Only then you will know what you need over what you want. You need yourself to become your own."

Made with the help of AI and Photoshop.

Size: 5000 x 3333
